<span class="prog-arrow">→</span><span class="prog-node n-mithril"><img src="/mite-be-wiki/img/ingots/mithril.png" alt="">Mithril</span>
<span class="prog-arrow">→</span><span class="prog-node n-nether">🔥 The Nether</span>
<span class="prog-arrow">→</span><span class="prog-node n-adam"><img src="/mite-be-wiki/img/ingots/adamantium.png" alt="">Adamantium</span>
